snippet.title: Skeletal Dance Party 💀 Alpha footage
snippet.description:
Alpha footage for Necromancer game Skeletal Dance Party. You are a foxgirl necromancer and your goal is to host the largest dance party ever for your skeletal pals!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/599160/Skeletal_Dance_Party/
Subscribe to our email list to get updates: http://eepurl.com/cBFWh5

Itch: https://catalopegames.itch.io/skeletal-dance-party
Read more at http://skeletaldance.party
